For a keto-compliant master recipe, the use of leeks is prioritized over onions. Leeks provide a similar depth of flavor with nearly half the net carbohydrate impact.13 Furthermore, the green tops of scallions can be used as a garnish to provide "oniony" aromatics without the sugar load associated with caramelized bulb onions.34
The Master Recipe Formulation: Starch-Free Keto Mushroom Puree
This recipe is engineered for a home chef seeking professional-level depth. It focuses on batch-searing for Maillard development and high-speed emulsification for fiber-based thickening.

